            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "The comment above says to use different unicode character, and this was correct before it was mistakenly changed in #38344. Also, before there was a trailing space, which looks nicer.\n\nBefore #38344:\n\n<img height=\"300\" alt=\"Image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/47e12b08-7810-48fd-a38a-5b1587b68708\" />\n\nThis PR:\n\n<img height=\"300\" alt=\"Image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/aa822511-07e9-42e8-9f24-0856aa9b924f\" />\n\nI guess it's better to just revert the change and keep the old variant?",
            "commit_id": "af2c3c80e198039e0a444dc0c7657d4ff231c474",
            "created_at": "2026-03-21T17:00:46Z",
